Hi Sean.  That&#39;s great that you are working on an All-In-One.  I would love
to see it too.  There is another All-In-One hand held by Digital Dowsing
called an Ovilus and it has speakjet capabilities using allophones and a
scaled-back dictionary, and EMF, digital dowsing rods,  and more.  



But I think it&#39;s great that you came up with a new idea!  

kristin



  _____  

From: EVP-ITC@yahoogroups.com [mailto:EVP-ITC@yahoogroups.com] On Behalf Of
seanjankowski1
Sent: Wednesday, June 25, 2008 10:11 AM
To: EVP-ITC@yahoogroups.com
Subject: [EVP-ITC] All In One Device



This is my first post. I was wondering if anyone had created an all in
one ITC EVP device. I know that researchers such as Seidle had created
the psychophone that seemed to cover many aspects of ITC but I have
yet to see all ways of communication in one device.

I have created an all in one design that covers most of the devices
used. If you wish I will share the design. 




